description.en: Bubble Network Token is an ERC20 Defi protocol built on the Ethereum network which boasts a fast transaction speed and low fees. Bubble Network has the vision to create a blockchain based ecosystem which incorporates products and services related to cryptocurrency such as staking/farming with the potential to link with other crypto assets involved in NFT (Non-Fungible Tokens), trading, farming, Governance, staking, Bonds, funds & etc.
